Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:23.15,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.15,0:01:26.07,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:31.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,暗闇に浮かんだ　棚引く淡い光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:36.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,まだ見ぬ未知の陽は　誰を照らし出すの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:41.16,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,愛しき My Buddy　哀しみくれても Don't worry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:46.13,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,何があっても　生き抜け That's all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:48.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Mysterious…　さぁ手を伸ばせ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:50.80,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Cyber world…　この闇を抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:53.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Take your hands…　脈打つ鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:56.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Danger Danger Danger　飛び出せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:02:00.31,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,見つめる世界の果て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:07.15,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,小さな胸に　憧れを　詰め込んだら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:17.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,琥珀の夢　約束のあの場所まで　いざ行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:24.46,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,キミを想う気持ちは　この空よりもでかい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:30.59,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,無限大　いつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:37.51,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:41.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Comment: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:23.15,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Comment: 0,0:01:23.15,0:01:26.07,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:31.20,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,黯淡的光暈  浮現於黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:36.41,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,未見未知的陽光  會將誰照亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:41.16,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,我親愛的伙伴  就算沉浸於悲傷也不慌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:46.13,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,不管發生什麼事  活下去才是唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:48.42,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Mysterious…  來伸出手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:50.80,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Cyber world…  穿過這片黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:53.01,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Take your hands…  衝擊全身的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:56.64,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Danger Danger Danger  起飛吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:02:00.31,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,緊盯著世界的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:07.15,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,當小小胸膛填滿了憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:17.08,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,琥珀之夢  朝著約定的地點出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:24.46,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,對你的關心關愛  比這天空更寬廣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:30.59,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,無限擴張  永無止境
Comment: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:37.51,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Comment: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:41.39,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
